title: In corsa contro il tempo
actors: Ralph Byrd, Irving Pichel, Ted Pearson, Jennifer Jones, Walter Miller, George Douglas, Kenneth Harlan, Robert Carson, Julian Madison, Ted Mapes, William Stahl, Robert Wayne, Joe McGuinn, Ken Terrell, Harry Humphrey
description: A mad doctor named Zanoff uses a drug to bring himself back from the dead after his execution in prison. Dick Tracy sets out to capture Zanoff before he can put his criminal gang back together again.
